race.comment: The $1 million Snippets. THE INSTRUCTOR (2) has a strong record over this six-furlong trip with three wins and two placings from seven starts and will have come on with that first-up run now under the belt. Handles all going and gets the reliable Waterhouse/Bott/Hyeronimus combination. Excellent winning prospects. HIDDEN WEALTH (1) goes well for hoop Berry who has three wins and a placing from just five rides. Ready to peak now fourth run back and rates a genuine top-three contender. PAYLINE (4) has placed two from two around this circuit and is usually thereabouts. A must for the multiples. SPYWIRE (6) is yet to miss a drum in three spins around this circuit and will be high on confidence following that last-start victory here. Not to be discounted. GIN A TONIC (8) has strung three wins together on the bounce this campaign and can feature again with any luck in running.
